---
layout: base.njk
title: Initiatives
summary: "Eight strategic programs advancing sovereign, human-centered technology for the common good."
---
<div class="section-head">
  <h1>Initiatives</h1>
  <p class="section-dek">Eight strategic programs advancing data sovereignty, sovereign AI, and values-based technology for the common good.</p>
</div>
<div class="initiatives">
{% for item in initiatives %}
  <section class="initiative">
    <h2 class="initiative-name">{{ item.name }}</h2>
    <p class="initiative-tagline">{{ item.tagline }}</p>
    <p class="initiative-desc">{{ item.description }}</p>
    {% if item.programs %}
    <ul class="initiative-programs">
      {% for program in item.programs %}<li>{{ program }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
  </section>
{% endfor %}
</div>